cracksql_query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT t2.id) FROM patient AS t1 INNER JOIN laboratory AS t2 ON t1.id = t2.id WHERE t2.cre >= 1.5 AND YEAR(CURDATE() - t1.birthday) < 70
pgsql_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT "t1"."id" ) FROM "patient" AS "t1" INNER JOIN "laboratory" AS "t2" ON "t1"."id" = "t2"."id" WHERE "t2"."cre" >= 1.5 AND EXTRACT( YEAR FROM AGE( CURRENT_DATE , "t1"."birthday" ) ) < 70

cracksql_query: SELECT DISTINCT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, TIMESTAMP('now'), `t2`.`birthday`)) + (CASE WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM TIMESTAMPDIFF(MONTH, TIMESTAMP('now'), `t2`.`birthday`)) > 0 OR EXTRACT(DAY FROM TIMESTAMPDIFF(DAY, TIMESTAMP('now'), `t2`.`birthday`)) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `age` FROM `player_attributes` AS `t1` INNER JOIN `player` AS `t2` ON `t1`.`player_api_id` = `t2`.`player_api_id` WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM `t1`.`date`) BETWEEN 2013 AND 2015 AND `t1`.`sprint_speed` >= 97;
pgsql_query: SELECT DISTINCT EXTRACT( YEAR FROM AGE( NOW( ) , "t2"."birthday" :: timestamp ) ) + ( CASE WHEN EXTRACT( MONTH FROM AGE( NOW( ) , "t2"."birthday" :: timestamp ) ) > 0 OR EXTRACT( DAY FROM AGE( NOW( ) , "t2"."birthday" :: timestamp ) ) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS "age" FROM "player_attributes" AS "t1" INNER JOIN "player" AS "t2" ON "t1"."player_api_id" = "t2"."player_api_id" WHERE EXTRACT( YEAR FROM "t1"."date" :: date ) BETWEEN 2013 AND 2015 AND "t1"."sprint_speed" >= 97
